Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak melakukan apa-apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba dia pingsan sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin dia punya penyakit kronis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak di antara mereka yang mudah sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita perlu memikirkan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noe, panggil Dokter Iz.
