Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan aku, bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sebut aku bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
