Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
