Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada hal tertentu yang bisa\Ndipahami beberapa orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku tahu luka kalian\Nbukan sekadar penyesalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat ini buktinya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jariku teriris!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aduh!\N- Lukanya dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
