Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tidak bilang dari tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, ada lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf karena merepotkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku mengacau lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulurkan tanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu orang dewasa, jadi tahan sedikit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beruang ini menakutkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Amumu, bukan beruang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sedang merawatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sero, siapa dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini Merim, perawat yang membantu Dokter Iz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam kenal, namanya Merim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sampai basah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama aku tidak melihatmu, Merim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini karena kalian tidak becus.
